title: Polymer Chemistry - A Practical Approach - Fred J. Davis
description:
Polymer Chemistry - A Practical Approach - Fred J. Davis (Oxford, 2004).pdf

ISBN 0 19 850309 1

Designed to appeal to chemists both working in and new to the area of polymer synthesis, this book contains detailed instructions for the preparation of a wide-range of polymers by a variety of different techniques. It also describes how this synthetic methodology can be applied to the development of new materials
